      <title>美联储主席鲍威尔新闻发布会精彩看点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-18/highlights-from-fed-chair-powell-s-news-conference-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔 (Jerome Powell) 就联邦公开市场委员会 (FOMC) 将联邦基金利率下调至 4.75% 至 5% 区间的决定发表讲话。以下是鲍威尔新闻发布会上的一些关键时刻。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-18/highlights-from-fed-chair-powell-s-news-conference-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 20:35:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝莱德的罗森伯格预计美联储将在未来两次降息 25 个基点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-18/blackrock-s-rosenberg-sees-two-25-bps-fed-cuts-ahead-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贝莱德系统多策略基金投资组合经理杰弗里·罗森伯格 (Jeffrey Rosenberg) 讨论了在联邦公开市场委员会决定将联邦基金利率下调至 4.75% 至 5% 区间后他如何投资固定收益。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-18/blackrock-s-rosenberg-sees-two-25-bps-fed-cuts-ahead-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 20:19:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>杜德利预计美联储 11 月将再次降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-18/dudley-expects-fed-to-cut-again-in-november-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约联邦储备银行前行长、彭博社观点专栏作家比尔·杜德利表示，他预计美联储将在 11 月再次降息。他说，美联储正在预测“软着陆”。他在“美联储决定”节目中发表了讲话。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-18/dudley-expects-fed-to-cut-again-in-november-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 20:13:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Brighton Park Capital 的 Gregoire 谈 IPO 前景</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-18/brighton-park-capital-s-gregoire-on-ipo-landscape</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Brighton Park Capital 创始合伙人 Mike Gregoire 与 Caroline Hyde 和 Ed Ludlow 一起讨论投资前景、市场动态以及他对 IPO 市场的展望。他在“彭博科技”上发表了讲话。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-18/brighton-park-capital-s-gregoire-on-ipo-landscape</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 20:09:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大德斯雅尔丹银行瞄准澳大利亚债券市场进行首次发行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/canada-s-desjardins-eyes-aussie-bond-market-for-debut-issuance</link>
      <description><![CDATA[北美最大的金融服务合作社德斯雅尔丹集团 (Desjardins Group) 正在准备在澳元债券市场首次发行债券，因为该集团寻求实现资金来源多元化，以满足其不断增长的贷款规模。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/canada-s-desjardins-eyes-aussie-bond-market-for-debut-issuance</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 20:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场参与者称美联储降息对信贷有利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/fed-cut-is-a-positive-for-credit-market-participants-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储周三宣布四年多来首次降息，将利率下调半个百分点，信贷衍生品利差随之收窄。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/fed-cut-is-a-positive-for-credit-market-participants-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 18:24:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储自 2020 年以来首次降息后，金价创下新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/gold-rises-after-us-fed-makes-first-rate-cut-since-2020</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔表示，继周三美国央行降息半个百分点后，决策者并不急于大幅降息，随后金价从历史高位回落。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/gold-rises-after-us-fed-makes-first-rate-cut-since-2020</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 18:02:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>黎巴嫩传呼机爆炸痕迹延伸至台湾、匈牙利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/trail-of-exploding-pagers-in-lebanon-leads-to-taiwan-hungary</link>
      <description><![CDATA[星期二下午 3 点 30 分左右，黎巴嫩传呼机爆炸，造成数千人死亡或致残，并引发人们对中东爆发新战争的担忧，爆炸地点就在布达佩斯一条高速公路和一座破旧火车站之间的一间小邮局。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/trail-of-exploding-pagers-in-lebanon-leads-to-taiwan-hungary</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 17:42:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储大幅降息未起到带头作用，新兴货币涨幅缩减</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/em-currencies-extend-rally-as-fed-nears-interest-rate-decision</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔表示，在美联储降息半个百分点后，决策者并不急于放松政策，因此新兴市场货币周三一度飙升，随后从盘中高点回落。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/em-currencies-extend-rally-as-fed-nears-interest-rate-decision</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 10:50:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储采取重大举措后，股票交易员“抛售新闻”：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储在将利率下调半个百分点后暗示并不急于放松政策，因此股市的上涨一度推动其升至历史新高，但随后遭遇挫折。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 22:37:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
